### Add Item to Cart
POST {{host}}/api/carts/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token {{token}}

{
    "items": [
        {
            "product": "camry-2009-xle",
            "quantity": "3"
        }
    ]
}

### Update Cart
PATCH {{host}}/api/carts/f79730ec-a786-4d55-bb04-97e2204f2279/
